**Summary:** Event Explorer is a real-time event stream visualization tool that allows users to view events and properties as they are triggered by specific users (identified by IP address, user ID, device ID, or user properties), enabling taxonomy exploration, instrumentation QA, and direct event addition to Amplitude charts.

